@page "/about-us"

<PageTitle>About Contoso - eShopLite</PageTitle>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">About Contoso</h1>
            
            <div class="lead mb-4">
                <p>Contoso is a leading retailer of electronics, apparel, and home goods. Founded in 1985, Contoso is committed to providing quality products and exceptional customer service.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>Our mission is to make shopping easy and enjoyable for everyone. We believe that every customer deserves access to high-quality outdoor gear that helps them explore the world with confidence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                    <p>To be the world's most trusted outdoor retailer, inspiring adventure and connecting people with nature through innovative products and exceptional experiences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="mb-3">Company Highlights</h3>
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h4 class="card-title">200+</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">Stores worldwide</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Since 1985</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">Serving outdoor enthusiasts</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h4 class="card-title">10M+</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">Happy customers</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="mb-3">Our Commitment</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-shield-check text-primary me-2"></i>Quality Products</h5>
                    <p>Every product in our catalog is carefully selected and tested to meet our high standards for quality, durability, and performance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-heart text-primary me-2"></i>Customer Service</h5>
                    <p>Our knowledgeable team is passionate about outdoor adventures and dedicated to helping you find the perfect gear for your needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-leaf text-success me-2"></i>Sustainability</h5>
                    <p>We're committed to environmental responsibility through sustainable sourcing, eco-friendly packaging, and supporting conservation efforts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-people text-primary me-2"></i>Community</h5>
                    <p>We actively support outdoor communities, local trails, and adventure education programs that inspire the next generation of explorers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
                <h5 class="alert-heading">With over 200 stores worldwide and a robust online presence, Contoso continues to innovate in the retail space.</h5>
                <p class="mb-0">Whether you're planning a weekend hike, training for a marathon, or gearing up for a multi-day expedition, we have the expertise and products to help you succeed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-5">
                <h4>Ready to Start Your Adventure?</h4>
                <p class="mb-3">Explore our products or get in touch with our team</p>
                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Shop Products</a>
                <a href="/careers" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Join Our Team</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>